quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,Closer and closer to the human being comes their judgment. Yet they are heedless and they turn away
  21,2,There has never come to them a renewed message from their Lord that they did not listen to without regard
  21,3,"While their hearts were distracted. The wrongdoers conceal their private meetings saying, “Is he more than a human like yourselves? Will you follow illusions with your eyes open?”"
  21,4,"Say, “My Lord knows each word in the heavens and on earth. He is the One Who hears and knows all things.”"
  21,5,"“No,” they say, \"A medley of dreams.\" \"No, he fabricated it\". \"No, he is a poet\". \"Let him bring us a sign like the ones that were sent to those in the past.”"
  21,6,"Before them, not one of the populations that We caused to perish believed. Will these believe"
  21,7,"Before you, those We sent were also only men to whom We granted inspiration. Ask those who have the message if you do not know"
  21,8,"Nor did We give them bodies that consumed no food, nor were they exempt from death"
  21,9,"In the end, We fulfilled Our promise to them, and We saved them and those whom We pleased, but We caused to perish those who transgressed beyond bounds"
  21,10,We have revealed for you a book in which is a message for you. Will you not use your intelligence